      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0670P0-04584'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0670P0_20050310_GCR_88' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Committee adjourned at one minute past five o'clock.
      </p>
